Usage: savePreference [-help] [-include_window_font] {[-directory {home current} | -file_name <string>]}

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
-directory {home current}     # Specify the directory path (enum, optional)
-file_name <string>           # Specify the saved filename (string, optional)
-include_window_font          # Include window and font setting
                              # (bool, optional)